To be honest the idea of Caulifla x Cabba actually appeals to me. I know some people won't agree but I actually think the ship is really cute and in many ways both of them have enough chemistry to get together. Cabba is humble warrior who wants to protect his family and planet from evil while also trying to impress Vegeta by getting stronger. Caulifla is a mouthy but secretly kind fighter with a desire to become stronger. Both of them are still kind people with a similar set of goals and a powerful ambition. It think the pair works just fine. Then again there's always Kale x Cabba. (^_^)
